title: Buying a name change, help me pick a name?
body:
Hey guys! I'm gonna buy a name change, I'm kinda bored of my current name. (Tried to spell Leviathan like 6 years ago and this is still my username for most games) I really want a Nautilus themed name because he's my favorite champion. I was thinking maybe "Captain Naut" but I'm not sure.  Could you guys give me some names themed around Nautilus? Thanks {{champion:111}}
Edit: Loving the suggestions so far :D What about DefinitelyNautNautilus?

replies.body: Haha, I edited my post and then saw yours. I was thinking the same thing
No, you were clearly copying from my post.  JK, but what about ImNautplayingmymain

Naut The Best.... get it? Not the best, Nautilus the best?

/edit CTE late game vs a heavy aa adc.. get thorn mail with cinderhulk and have gromp buff going. You can kill an adc on Naut without putting much effort. Maybe sit there and send a text and look up the ad will be dead.
Name is taken haha, but yeah I love building pure tank Naut and still getting kills
NautMyJob...guys? anything, well i tried idk if it that good tbh

Don't make a name with any LCS Initals in it even if you are just representing the team like wearing a Patriots jersey to a Patriots game.. Or else people will start making retarded comments like..

Oh... look a fanboy
Oh.. look a fake Tsm..
Oh .. look a wannabe

Stupid shit like that and that's before the game starts.

DroppingAnchor
TitanOfTheDeep
GettinNauttyInHere
DeepSpaceDiver- astronaut themed
NautANautilusMain


I like nautilus too :D and cinderhulk makes him viable :D
